---
<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-8">
          Bridging the gap between <span class="italic">Analytics</span> and Code.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            With a Master's in Data Science, I bridge the critical gap between raw technical data modeling and strategic product management. My core specialization lies in unit economics—specifically focusing on LTV:CAC optimization.
          </p>
          <p>
            My foundational experience spans across the OTT and tech landscapes in India, where I've successfully designed monetization frameworks and built market-entry strategies for heavy vertical-specific SaaS applications.
          </p>
          <p>
            I believe that engineered products must be commercially viable. I transform market-entry research into actionable product roadmaps that scale efficiently.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-accent">MS</div>
            <div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mt-2">Data Science</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-accent">100%</div>
            <div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mt-2">Data Focused</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-3xl overflow-hidden grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" 
            alt="Product Manager Portrait" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-950 p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex items-center justify-center text-center">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter">Certified Product Leader</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
